declare_parcel_as_script_with_stdin <<'/---'
Document all globals, functions, and aliases declared by @{*-glob}.
/---

# ....................{ GLOBALS                            }....................
:string_global ZESHY_HELP_GLOB <<'/---'
Glob matching high-level features in alias, function, and global documentation.

== Match Groups ==

This glob captures the following substrings from such documentation:

* `${match[1]}`, the prototype prefixing such documentation suffixed by a
  *blank line* (i.e., two consecutive newlines, optionally delimited by zero or
  more tab or space characters).
* `${match[2]}`, the non-prototype remainder of such documentation --
  presumably in AsciiDoc format.

This glob attempts to match _no_ low-level syntax in such documentation.
/---

# --------------------( WASTELANDS                         )--------------------
